Increase of landowners, but how. 55.9% did own less than 1 ha. 97.27% less than 10 ha, covering in all only 22.13% of land. The 58 farms (0,17%) with more than 500 ha owned 61.81% of land. Many small owners thus continued in parallel to work as wage earners or in factories.

Renting: 80,29% of renters worked not more than 3 ha. thus overall 8.54% of rented land.

